snippet.title: NARAKA: BLADEPOINT - Xbox Game Pass Announcement Trailer - Xbox & Bethesda Games Showcase 2022
snippet.description: Join 10 million players in the mythical action Battle Royale. NARAKA: BLADEPOINT is coming to Xbox Series X|S, Windows Store on June 23. Included with Game Pass at launch.
